Sentencas: GdBaCO2O5+x (GBCO) was evaluated as a cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: GdBaCO2O5+x layered perovskite temperature solid oxide fuel as an intermediate cell cathode

Sentencas: A porous layer of GBCO was deposited on an anode-supported fuel cell consisting of a 15 mu m thick electrolyte of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) prepared by dense screen-printing and a Ni-YSZ cermet as an anode (Ni-YSZ/YSZ/GBCO).
Titulo: GdBaCO2O5+x layered perovskite temperature solid oxide fuel as an intermediate cell cathode

Sentencas: Values of power density of 150 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C and ca.
Titulo: GdBaCO2O5+x layered perovskite temperature solid oxide fuel as an intermediate cell cathode

Sentencas: 250 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C are reported for this standard configuration using 5% of H-2 in nitrogen as fuel.
Titulo: GdBaCO2O5+x layered perovskite temperature solid oxide fuel as an intermediate cell cathode

Sentencas: An intermediate porous layer of YSZ was introduced between the electrolyte and the cathode improving the performance of the cell.
Titulo: GdBaCO2O5+x layered perovskite temperature solid oxide fuel as an intermediate cell cathode

Sentencas: Values for power density of 300 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C and ca.
Titulo: GdBaCO2O5+x layered perovskite temperature solid oxide fuel as an intermediate cell cathode

Sentencas: 500 mW cm-2 at 800 degrees C in this configuration were achieved.
Titulo: GdBaCO2O5+x layered perovskite temperature solid oxide fuel as an intermediate cell cathode
